{"tid":679350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚心香港人唔撚好老馮要服務行業人笑啦","createTime":"2018-05-26T19:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T11:32:41.000Z","uid":26553,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a5674cfa2041c0f040b90ee357f1f2b77d2f5b","tid":679350,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T19:06:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母係香港做服務業低賤過所有職業<br />\n人工低 地位低 工時長 壓力大 <br />\n但係要求渣巴士 待應 sales既對客職業人笑<br />\n屌你老母不如你笑比我睇呀？ 痴鳩線 <br />\n去幾日日本話 人地點點點好服務<br />\n人地成個民族壓抑自己做出黎所謂服務 轉個面咪又係屌鳩你 <br />\n<br />\n不如投訴香港人唔笑既香港人講下你地平時返工有幾撚好態度 點撚樣下下對住人笑呀？ <br />\n果d咩撚野神秘客人簡直係垃圾中垃圾 完美演繹渣著雞毛當令箭 一句說話就令成間鋪既人努力付諸流水 <br />\n我估我唔撚想開開心心做人？ 日日對住班西客 人手又唔夠 個個葉問咁樣返工 人工又唔加 放左工又要諗比家用 拍拖又要洗錢 仲要儲錢買二十年唔食唔飲既樓 <br />\n你教我點撚樣下下笑比你睇呀 仆街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets